===============================================================================
PATCH: DirectXTK Model Viewer - Simple Command Line Auto-Load
===============================================================================
This patch adds minimal command line support to DirectXTKModelViewer, allowing
a model path to be passed as argv[1]. The model is loaded automatically on the
first Tick() call.

Example:
   DirectXTKModelViewer.exe "C:\path\to\UNIT450.cmo"
===============================================================================


FILE: Game.h  (around line ~60)

Add this public member:

    wchar_t m_cmdLineModel[MAX_PATH] = {};



-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FILE: Main.cpp
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Inside wWinMain, AFTER g_game->Initialize(), add:

    // Store model path from command line (if any)
    int argc = 0;
    LPWSTR* argv = CommandLineToArgvW(GetCommandLineW(), &argc);
    if (argv && argc > 1)
    {
        wcscpy_s(g_game->m_cmdLineModel, argv[1]);
    }
    if (argv)
        LocalFree(argv);



-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FILE: Game.cpp
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

At the *beginning* of Game::Tick(), insert:

    // Auto-load a model passed on the command line
    if (*m_cmdLineModel)
    {
        OnFileOpen(m_cmdLineModel);
        *m_cmdLineModel = 0; // Clear after first use
    }




===============================================================================
BUILD INSTRUCTIONS
===============================================================================

1. git clone https://github.com/walbourn/directxtkmodelviewer
2. cd directxtkmodelviewer
3. git submodule update --init --recursive
4. Apply the edits to Game.h, Main.cpp, Game.cpp
5. Open DirectXTKModelViewer_Desktop_2019.sln in Visual Studio
6. Select "Release x64"
7. Build solution
8. The compiled viewer will be located in:
      Bin/Desktop_2019/x64/Release/DirectXTKModelViewer.exe


===============================================================================
USAGE
===============================================================================

DirectXTKModelViewer.exe                       # Opens file dialog
DirectXTKModelViewer.exe "C:\model.cmo"        # Auto-loads model
DirectXTKModelViewer.exe "C:\model.sdkmesh"
DirectXTKModelViewer.exe "C:\model.vbo"
